    "causal_summary": "Phase 001 of packet 035 (unified command-contract architecture). Closes F-014, F-025 and builds the rollout mechanism (plan-review GAP-47). Two jobs, both prerequisites for safely landing any rewrite: make the 033 behavior-benchmark trustworthy as the acceptance harness, and build the per-command feature-flag rollout kill-switch with a byte-identical pre-035 fallback. Absorbs plan-review gaps GAP-01/03/06/08/14/37/38/39/40/45/47/49.",
